{"tid":560394,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"墨魚丸鯁喉女生 搶救26日不治","createTime":"2018-02-14T05:00:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T05:13:03.000Z","uid":40892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0a98c1de54418e0cd6edddc1bef0a2d6f279f923","tid":560394,"uid":40892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/14/125948_890b28d25cfa755b39e04030c6be0cba.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F14%2F125948_890b28d25cfa755b39e04030c6be0cba.png&h=909ceceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n8歲小三女生，上月在元朗學校小食部食墨魚丸時鯁喉( <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Bd7aaG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Bd7aaG&d=S0JqnjFrO9tkynOqOojc%2B8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=f207aef3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Bd7aaG</a> )，留院搶救26日後，於前日(周一)不治。<br />\n女童姓周，於在元朗欖口村路佛教陳榮根紀念學校讀書。上月18日，她在小息時間，在小食部購買墨魚丸進食，期間鯁喉暈倒，送院搶救。留院期間，女童的父母每日也到兒童深切治療部探望女兒，愁眉不展。周父做財務策劃，於女兒出事後停工。他曾表示，意外沒人想發生，因此沒有怪責學校。當時他引述醫生指，女兒骾喉達20分鐘，送院後才將墨魚丸取出。"},{"pid":"85b6ed72359461daae56f6d07e86b4b3fdff2759","tid":560394,"uid":32227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:02:12.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"87ae55f93e06c639b28a347643f767f9c3c1e2bf","tid":560394,"uid":136760,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:06:02.000Z","msg":"肯定小息就完比啲仆街老師催啦 手停腳停口停排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cacc53cc3734382a77bf58b4cfe042c1a5092a35","tid":560394,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:08:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c9e49016d8e2dbe5d9e2ad83be1d04ce263ea41","tid":560394,"uid":120908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:10:25.000Z","msg":"明顯學校問題，正常出事即刻call，5分鐘內白車就到，一定係拖左一陣見大撚獲先call車，自私學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca0e3d2f71